          "script": "Latn",
          "is_primary": false
        }
      ],
      "remarks": "Given the rank of General in the FARDC in December 2004. As of June 2011,\ndetained in Makala Prison in Kinshasa. As of 25 March 2011, the High Military Court in\nKinshasa opened a trial against Kakwavu for war crimes. In November 2014, convicted by a\nDRC military court to ten years in prison for rape, murder, and torture. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
