      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "CDi.008",
      "remarks": "A military leader of the Mouvement du 23 Mars (M23) group operating in\nthe Democratic Republic of the Congo. In Uganda as of late 2014. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
