      "remarks": "While president of the Fédération des entreprises congolaises (FEC) in\nAru territory, Dieudonné Ozia Mazio is believed to have died in Ariwara on 23 September\n2008. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
