      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "CDi.036",
      "remarks": "Longtime member of the ADF (CDe.001), Baluku used to be the second in command to ADF founder Jamil Mukulu (CDi.015) until he took over after FARDC military operation Sukola I in 2014.",
