        ]
      },
      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "QDe.001",
      "remarks": "Associated with Jemaah Islamiyah (JI) (QDe.092). Current leader is\nRadulan Sahiron (QDi.208). Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008)\nwas concluded on 21 Jun. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
      "raw_source_data": {
        "source_format": "xml",
