      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "QDe.118",
      "remarks": "Associated with Hafiz Muhammad Saeed (QDi.263) who is the leader of\nLashkar-e-Tayyiba. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 1822 (2008) was\nconcluded on 8 Jun. 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 24 November 2020. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.  INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
