      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "QDi.309",
      "remarks": "Has provided facilitation and financial services to Al-Qaida (QDe.004).\nAssociated with Harakatul Jihad Islami (QDe.130), Jaish-I-Mohammed (QDe.019), and\nAl-Akhtar Trust International (QDe.121).  Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2253 (2015) was concluded on 21 Feb. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 8 November 2022. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
