        "effective_date": "2015-07-01",
        "is_indefinite": true,
        "last_updated": [
          "\n        ",
          "\n      "
        ]
      },
      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "SSi.003",
      "remarks": "Appointed commander of the Sudan People’s Liberation Army in Opposition\n(SPLA-IO) Special Division in December 2014. His forces have been engaged in attacks\nagainst civilians. In February 2014, forces under his command attacked United Nations\ncamps, hospitals, churches, and schools, engaging in widespread rape, torture, and the\ndestruction of property, in an attempt to flush out civilians, soldiers, and policemen\nallied with the government. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
      "raw_source_data": {
        "source_format": "xml",
        "source_specific_fields": {
          "un:dataId": "6908461",
          "un:versionNum": "1",
          "un:entityType": "individual"
        }
      }
    },
    {
