      "remarks": "Roshan Money Exchange stores and transfers funds to support Taliban\nmilitary operations and narcotics trade in Afghanistan. Owned by Ahmed Shah Noorzai\nObaidullah (TAi.166). INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
