      "reference_number": "TAi.100",
      "remarks": "Alternative title: Sar Muallim. Reconciled after the fall of the Taliban\nregime, and assumed duties under the new Government on district level in Kunduz\nProvince. Confirmed assassinated by Taliban on 9 November 2008. Review pursuant to\nSecurity Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 27 Jul. 2010. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
      "raw_source_data": {
        "source_format": "xml",
        "source_specific_fields": {
