        ]
      },
      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "TAi.147",
      "remarks": "Member of a Taliban Council that coordinates the collection of zakat\n(Islamic tax) from Baluchistan Province, Pakistan. Head of Taliban Financial Commission\nas at mid-2013. Associated with Mullah Mohammed Omar (TAi.004). Served as Omar's\nprincipal finance officer and one of his closest advisors. Belongs to Ishaqzai\ntribe. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
      "raw_source_data": {
