          "\n        ",
          "\n        ",
          "\n      "
        ]
      },
      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "TAi.148",
      "remarks": "Has managed a drug trafficking network in Helmand Province, Afghanistan.\nHas regularly traveled to Pakistan. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
