        "is_indefinite": true,
        "last_updated": [
          "\n        ",
          "\n        ",
          "\n        ",
          "\n      "
        ]
      },
      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "TAi.154",
      "remarks": "Taliban financier. Owns businesses in Japan and frequently travels to\nDubai, United Arab Emirates, and Japan. As of 2009, facilitated Taliban activities,\nincluding through recruitment and the provision of logistical support. Believed to be in\nthe Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Belongs to Noorzai tribe. Brother of Faizullah\nKhan Noorzai (TAi.153). Father’s name is Haji Akhtar Muhammad. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
      "raw_source_data": {
        "source_format": "xml",
        "source_specific_fields": {
