        "effective_date": "2011-10-04",
        "is_indefinite": true,
        "last_updated": [
          "\n        ",
          "\n      "
        ]
      },
      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "TAi.155",
      "remarks": "Key commander in the Haqqani Network (TAe.012) under Sirajuddin\nJallaloudine Haqqani (TAi.144). Taliban Shadow Governor for Orgun District, Paktika\nProvince as of early 2010. Operated a training camp for non-Afghan fighters in Paktika\nProvince. Has been involved in the transport of weapons to Afghanistan. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
      "raw_source_data": {
        "source_format": "xml",
