        "effective_date": "2012-01-06",
        "is_indefinite": true,
        "last_updated": [
          "\n        ",
          "\n        ",
          "\n      "
        ]
      },
      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "TAi.158",
      "remarks": "Senior Taliban member as at 2011 with financial duties, including raising funds\n                on behalf of the leadership. Has provided logistical support for Taliban operations\n                and channeled proceeds from drug trafficking to arms purchases. Has acted as\n                secretary to Taliban leader Mullah Mohammed Omar (TAi.004) and as his messenger at\n                senior-level meetings of the Taliban. Also associated with Gul Agha Ishakzai\n                (TAi.147). Member of Mullah Mohammed Omar’s (TAi.004) inner circle during the\n                Taliban regime. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
      "raw_source_data": {
        "source_format": "xml",
        "source_specific_fields": {
          "un:dataId": "2981821",
          "un:versionNum": "1",
          "un:entityType": "individual"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "https://www.ammitto.org/entry/un/TAi.159",
      "entity_id": "https://www.ammitto.org/entity/un/TAi.159",
      "authority": {
        "id": "un",
        "name": "United Nations",
        "country_code": "UN"
      },
      "regime": {
        "name": "Taliban",
        "code": "TALIBAN"
      },
      "effects": [
        {
          "effect_type": "asset_freeze",
          "scope": "full"
        },
        {
          "effect_type": "travel_ban",
          "scope": "full"
        }
      ],
      "period": {
        "listed_date": "2012-01-06",
        "effective_date": "2012-01-06",
        "is_indefinite": true,
        "last_updated": [
          "\n        ",
          "\n        ",
          "\n      "
        ]
      },
      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "TAi.159",
      "remarks": "Key commander of the Haqqani Network (TAe.012), which is based in\nAfghanistan/Pakistan border area. Acts as deputy, spokesperson and advisor for Haqqani\nNetwork senior leader Sirajuddin Jallaloudine Haqqani (TAi.144). Liaises with the\nTaliban Supreme Council. Has travelled abroad. Liaises with and provides Taliban\ncommanders in Ghazni Province, Afghanistan, with money, weapons, communications\nequipment and supplies. Reportedly deceased as of 2013. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
      "raw_source_data": {
