        ]
      },
      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "TAi.164",
      "remarks": "Chief of suicide operations for the Haqqani Network (TAe.012) under\nSirajuddin Jallaloudine Haqqani (TAi.144) and in charge of all operations in Kabul,\nTakhar, Kunduz and Baghlan provinces. Oversees training of suicide attackers and\nprovides instructions on how to construct improvised explosives devices\n(IEDs). INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
      "raw_source_data": {
