      },
      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "TAi.165",
      "remarks": "Owner of Rahat Ltd. (TAe.013). Involved in the supply of weapons for Taliban, including improvised explosive devices (IED). Arrested in 2012 and in custody in Afghanistan as of January 2013. Associated with Rahat Ltd. (TAe.013). INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
