      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "TAi.166",
      "remarks": "Owns and operates the Roshan Money Exchange (TAe.011). Provided financial\nservices to Ghul Agha Ishakzai (TAi.147) and other Taliban in Helmand Province.\nAlternative title is Maulavi. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
