        "effective_date": "2014-03-19",
        "is_indefinite": true,
        "last_updated": [
          "\n        ",
          "\n      "
        ]
      },
      "status": "active",
      "reference_number": "TAi.168",
      "remarks": "Believed to be in Afghanistan/Pakistan border area. Taliban Shadow Deputy\nGovernor and operational commander in Zabul Province, Afghanistan, responsible for the\nlaying of improvised explosive devices and the organisation of suicide attacks. Physical\ndescription: height: 180 cm; weight: approximately 90 kg; build: athletic build; eye\ncolour: brown; hair colour: red; complexion: medium brown. Distinguishing physical\nmarks: large round face, full beard, and walks with a limp due to plastic prosthesis in\nplace of his left lower leg. Ethnic background: Pashtun; Belongs to Tokhi tribe,\nBarkozai sub-tribe (alternative tribe spelling: Torchi). Barkozai (alternative tribe\nspelling: Bakorzai, باکورزی) sub-tribe, Kishta Barkorzai (lower Barkorzai) clan. Marital\nStatus: married. Father’s name: Agha Mohammad. Brother’s name: Humdullah. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
      "raw_source_data": {
        "source_format": "xml",
        "source_specific_fields": {
          "un:dataId": "3035783",
          "un:versionNum": "1",
          "un:entityType": "individual"
        }
      }
    },
